title: Overpowered and Underpaid: An OP Swordmaster Turns Hit Streamer
description: “Work—that’s the true grave of life…” With a heavy sigh, exploited guild employee Makoto Tanaka trudges into yet another dungeon. Per protocol, he starts a stream for company records—only this time, he accidentally sets it to PUBLIC.
author: Genkotsu Kumano
